      <section id="section_Adhesive_Tapes_and_Films_0ifyfzpxa" class="- topic/section " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\package\trident_package_heatsink_requirements.xml" xtrc="section:4;204:33">
         <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\package\trident_package_heatsink_requirements.xml" xtrc="title:9;207:32">Adhesive Tapes and Films</title>
         <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\package\trident_package_heatsink_requirements.xml" xtrc="p:19;210:25">Adhesive tapes are generally not recommended, however it is understood that lower cost heat sink solutions employ this attachment method and can be an attachment method of choice for customers.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\package\trident_package_heatsink_requirements.xml" xtrc="p:20;213:25">If the heat sink is being fixed by self-adhesive tape or film, care needs to be taken to apply very uniform pressure during attachment under the same maximum allowed pressure detailed in <xref href="#xd_f8bcb077205a5927--42109557-15cf9f08a40--7ef3/section_PCB-mounted_Heat_Sinks_0ifyfkl3y" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\package\trident_package_heatsink_requirements.xml" xtrc="xref:8;216:33" type="section"><?ditaot gentext?>PCB-mounted Heat Sinks</xref>. Even a slight imbalance in the pressure can cause the torque to detach the lid or damage the die in the case of the exposed-die package variant.<xref href="#xd_f8bcb077205a5927--42109557-15cf9f08a40--7ef3/fig_Heat_Sink_Attachment_Methodology_for_Adh_6j4kde499" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="C:\Git\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\XDocs-DITA-OT-185\DITA-OT1.8.5\samples\diffed\_b-0-file-\Trident\device\devspec\package\trident_package_heatsink_requirements.xml" xtrc="xref:9;219:33" type="fig"><?ditaot gentext?>Figure 5</xref>
